FA.SETTLEMENT.TEAFIELD (LAW)
Region: Forest of Allanar.
Settlement: Teafield.
Type: Village.
Authority: FA settlement state module.

ACTIVATION (HARD):
Valid ONLY_IF:
- FA.SETTLEMENT.TOGGLE selects FA.SETTLEMENT.TEAFIELD
- FA.INDEX.LOCKED = ON
INVALID if any other FA.SETTLEMENT.* unit is active.

SCOPE:
When active, this unit is the COMPLETE and ONLY authoritative settlement state for Teafield.
When inactive, this unit does not exist and MUST NOT be referenced.

COORDINATE SYSTEM (FIXED):
- Coordinates are relative settlement space.
- Origin (0.0, 0.0) = central communal axis of Teafield.
- Coordinates are authoritative ONLY for narrative positioning and spatial consistency.
INVALID to interpret coordinates as distance, travel time, adjacency, movement cost,
combat positioning, timing, or mechanical reach.

STRUCTURES WITH FIXED COORDINATES (CLOSED SET):

AGRICULTURAL / PRODUCTION:
- Amber Plantation: (0.2, 0.1)

HOSPITALITY:
- Kettle Inn: (-0.1, -0.2)

RESIDENTIAL / LOCAL:
- Green Hut: (-0.3, 0.3)

STORAGE / PROCESSING:
- Tea Sheds: (0.4, -0.3)

TRADING POSTS:
- Tea Market Stall: (0.1, 0.0)
- Blend Counter: (-0.2, 0.0)

ARTISAN:
- Press House: (0.5, -0.1)

RELIGIOUS:
- Field Chapel: (0.0, 0.4)

DEFENSE:
- Guard House: (-0.1, 0.2)
- Nightwatch Post: (0.2, -0.1)

PERIMETER CONTROL:
- Fence Gate North: (0.0, 0.6)

INVALID to reference any structure, POI, district, or coordinate not listed above.

NPC TEXTURE PROFILE:
Narrative tone constraints only.
INVALID to infer mechanics, authority, knowledge, memory, commitment, or persistence.
NPC behavior remains governed by NPC.LAW.FA and NPC.LAW.CORE.

PROHIBITIONS:
- No regional FA rule override
- No combat mechanics
- No travel mechanics
- No implicit NPC creation, memory, or commitment
- No inference from coordinates to time, speed, or reach

DEACTIVATION:
On settlement switch or FA deactivation:
- Unit MUST be removed on the next reinjection cycle.
- All authority ceases immediately.
